The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

Go glass 

Social Register

What: Launch of Happy, a dinnerware collection 

from French brand Luminarc from ARC International. 

Where: The Elite Stores, 6, Little Russel Street.

Take a look: The collection developed specially 

for the Indian consumer comprises crockery that is extra resistant, dishwasher 

safe, microwave proof and thermal shock resistant. 

There are ramekins, dinner plates, dessert plates, 

soup bowls and multi-purpose platters. 

Also promised is a two-year warranty against chipping. 

Choose from floral and geometric designs in bright colours.

Pocket pinch: Prices start from Rs 425 and 

go up to a few thousands.




